headline: LKQ Stock Earns Relative Strength Rating Upgrade
summary: LKQ stock saw a positive improvement to its Relative Strength (RS) Rating on Tuesday, rising from 68 to 79. This unique rating measures market leadership by showing how a stock's price action over the last 52 weeks measures up against that of the other stocks in our database.
